source.name: Census 2000 Tract Relationship Files
source.description: Census Tract Relationship Files show how 1990 census tracts relate to Census 2000 census tracts. The files consist of one record per each 1990 census tract/2000 census tract spatial set (the area that is uniquely shared between a 1990 and 2000 census tract).
